title: Team Tainan The National Games Kaohsiung 2015 Flag Presentation (Tainan City Government)
text: ( Source : Tainan City Government ) On Oct. 15, team Tainan flag presentation of The National Games Kaohsiung 2015 was held at the Tainan City Hall Square . Mayor Lai presented the flag to Liou Fucai, the board director of Tainan Municipal
